headline: RBC Raises Prologis (PLD) Target as Industrial Real Estate Outlook Improves
summary: Prologis, Inc. (NYSE:PLD) is included among the 14 Best Real Estate Stocks to Buy According to Hedge Funds. On February 2, RBC Capital analyst Michael Carroll raised his price recommendation on Prologis, Inc. (NYSE:PLD) to $135 from $132.
